the Tcl/Tk scripting language and have been tested on Linux, Windows
and Mac OS *).

Windows- and Mac OS users do not need to do anything about Tcl/Tk,
but Linux users may have to install a package, e.g.  for
Debian-based systems:

  sudo apt install tk

French and Dutch localizations are fairly complete, but with most
other languages you will still encounter many untranslated strings.

